  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个WebSocket连接的状态图，描述从建立连接到最终断开的过程。初始状态应该是等待认证消息，然后进入代理状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "wait",
        "proxied",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是[*]，然后到新连接触发进入\"Wait for auth message\"状态。这个等待状态如果收到认证消息就转到代理状态，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "wait",
        "proxied",
        "New connection",
        "Auth message received"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外，等待状态需要有个超时机制——10秒没收到认证就直接断开。代理状态也可能因为连接终止而断开，或者保持自循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "wait",
        "disconnected",
        "proxied",
        "Time out after 10s",
        "Websocket connection terminated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主要状态节点画出来：\"Wait for auth message\"、\"Connection proxied\"和\"Disconnected\"，然后用[*]标记起点和终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "wait",
        "proxied",
        "disconnected",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "状态命名用简洁的别名吧，比如wait、proxied、disconnected，这样图看起来更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "wait",
        "proxied",
        "disconnected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。现在连接关系是：[*] → wait（新连接触发），wait → proxied（收到认证），wait → disconnected（10秒超时），proxied → disconnected（连接终止），还有proxied的自循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "wait",
        "proxied",
        "disconnected",
        "New connection",
        "Auth message received",
        "Time out after 10s",
        "Websocket connection terminated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，disconnected之后应该能回到结束状态吧？就是流程的终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "disconnected",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "补上这条线：disconnected → [*]。现在所有状态流转都完整了——从建立连接、认证等待、代理转发，到各种断开情况的终态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "disconnected",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    }
